<div id='TagCloud' style="display: none; width: 400px" class="Pro-Popup">	
    <h1 class="Sidebar-Title" style="text-align: center;">Disorganizer&trade; Tag Cloud by &copy;Chandru</h1>
    <p>The Disorganizer&trade; Tag Cloud is inspired by <a target="_blank" href="http://www.wordle.net/">Wordle</a> and 
        <a target="_blank" href="http://www.tagcloud.com/">TagCloud</a>.</p> 
    <br />
    <p>Both of those sites do not give you an on-the-fly
        cloud generation functionality which can be put into a blog, or a profile. Nor do they allow you to click on the tags and show hover animation on the tags,
        so I wrote this one using tools and classes in the .net 
        System.Drawing namespace.</p> 
    <br />
    <p>Go <a href="/Disorganizer/Tinker" target="_blank">here</a> to see what features you have with this utility.
        Hit F5 key or Refresh button on the browser to see a new Cloud :)
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>Thanks to <a href="http://www.cooltext.com/">Cooltext</a> for the nice fonts, and to <a href="http://www.stackoverflow.com/">StackOverflow</a>
        community for the invaluable answers.</p> 
